---
title: Tex Mex Bean, Chicken & Avocado Cos Salad with Roast Tomato Salsa & Corn Chips
description: Say hello to your newest salad obsession! It’s loaded with honey-tossed spiced beans, creamy avo, chargrilled capsicum relish,
and crispy corn chips for that perfect crunch. It’s fresh, fun, and fabulously fuss-free. Taco night just got an upgrade!
